ED_Title: Observer status for the International Conference of Asian Political Parties in the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText:
At its 62nd plenary meeting, on 13 December 2016, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Sixth Committee. 

(See A/71/526, A/71/PV.62)
